snippet.title: NEW OFFICIAL TRAILER! I Had A Plan! Upcoming Roguelike Semi-Autobattler inspired by D&D/Pathfinder!
snippet.description:
WISHLIST:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2375280?utm_source=yt1

The New and Improved Official Trailer!

A little early development preview of I Had A Plan!, an upcoming Roguelike Semi-Autobattler inspired by TTRPGs like D&D and Pathfinder. Wishlist on Steam now!

Follow me on Twitter for updates: https://twitter.com/BenevolentB_dev
